  "moveStrategies": {
    "cursed-strikes": [
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "center",
        "content": "[b]Skill Overview[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "content": "Description"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "content": [
          "Vessel first strike a pose with 30f startup, upon inputing the skill.",
          "Then the user will lunge forward around 28-32 studs, while a projectile hitbox spawned in a travel at the same speed;",
          "Notably, the user can not curve the skill, and the hitbox is active for 55f.",
          "On whiff, Vessel suffers a -25f whiff endlag; On block, Vessel instead suffers a -46f block endlag.",
          "Finally, on hit, Vessel gain 113f of Self Stun and inflict 161f of Target Stun during and after the attack barrage;",
          "this give Vessel a +48f Advantage against the target."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "video",
        "src": "../../medias/videos/NoNeutralCS.webm",
        "align": "right",
        "width": "50%",
        "controls": false
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "left",
        "content": "[b]Neutral Application[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "align": "left",
        "content": [
          "[color=hsl(0, 80%, 30%)]DO NOT[/color] use this skill in Neutral.",
          "The move is extremly easy to interrupt on prediction or even reaction thanks to its lengthy 30f startup."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "video",
        "src": "../../medias/videos/NoNeutral2CS.webm",
        "align": "left",
        "width": "45%",
        "controls": false
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "right",
        "content": "[b]Extremely Punishable if Blocked[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "align": "right",
        "content": [
          "Especially when you risk getting the move blocked and get a massive 46f block endlag, which anyone with half a braincell",
          "can punish it. Plus the fact that, you just also wasted your best damaging tool and mixup option."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "left",
        "content": "[b]Pure Combo Tool[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "align": "left",
        "content": [
          "Cursed Strikes exist solely to do combo and nothing else, dealing a decent 17.5 damage,",
          "and it lasts pretty long too, which can help with [b]Cooldown Stalling[/b]. Plus,",
          "it is the only safe move in Vessel's kit"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "center",
        "content": "[b]Strategies[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "content": "[b]Cooldown Stalling[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "content": [
          "As mentioned earlier, the skill on hit last quite long, so it would be decent in stalling cooldown."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "content": "[b]'Neutral' Cursed Strikes[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "content": [
          "It is so stupid for anyone to attempt to throw this move out of Neutral.",
          "And that's when this 'strategy' be viable with three layers of asterisk.",
          "The idea is that it is so stupid, that it becomes a suprise option that you can get away [b]if it lands[/b].",
          "It is kinda similar to Locust Guy's 'Clever Mixup' but inferior in everyway"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "content": "[b]Sauceless[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "content": [
          "Beside being an extremly generic Grab move that deal damage and stall cooldown.",
          "This skill has nothing of notes that would be helpful for the user to know"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "center",
        "content": "[b]Others[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type": "video",
        "src": "../../medias/videos/MeleeIframeDiffedCS.webm",
        "align": "right",
        "width": "35%",
        "controls": false
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "left",
        "content": "[b]Melee Type Grab[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "align": "left",
        "content": [
          "This is all Melee type, so watch out for enemies move that give them Melee Iframes, you don't want to waste your skill.",
          "Furthermore, it is also very counterable (obviously).",
          "",
          "",
          ""
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "video",
        "src": "../../medias/videos/NoExplosionIframeCS.webm",
        "align": "left",
        "width": "35%",
        "controls": false
      },
      {
        "type":"heading",
        "align": "left",
        "content": "[b]Only Melee and Bullet Iframes on Hit[/b]"
      },
      {
        "type":"paragraph",
        "align": "left",
        "content": [
          "Cursed Strikes on Hit will give Vessel Melee and Bullet Iframes for the total duration equal to the self stun.",
          "This, however, means that the skill can be diffed [b]even on Hit[/b] by uncancellable delayed Explosion moves such as ",
          "Cursed Partners' Outburst or Blood Manipulator's Blood Mine."
        ],
        "author": "Deptr"
      }
    ],
